As part of my salvager training,
I'm being made to help out
at this port all day.

rows.label: tlk006101_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Running back and forth
all over the place...
Working is pretty tough...

rows.label: tlk006101_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But salvaging is all about
diving, right? Is there
really any point to this?
